      "content": "The certainty of the timing is precisely what makes this situation so delicate, and I have to be clear: we are not operating on a fixed timeline. The current movements are a calculated pressure application, designed to force a response before any definitive escalation occurs. Waiting a few weeks would be an act of profound strategic vulnerability, as the opposing side is clearly banking on our hesitation to solidify their gains. We need to move decisively now to dictate the terms of the next phase, not react to them.",
